{
  "data": {"from_network_fetcher": true},
  "schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "from_network_fetcher": {"type": "boolean"}
    },
    "required": ["from_network_fetcher"]
  }
}
</tool_call>

            Now that we've validated the data, I'll proceed with the final step of parsing the data into an unspecified format using the data_processing_parser tool.

<tool_call>data_processing_parser
